 "Title":"Relates to the offices and departments that the department of health shall consult with for the traumatic brain injury program",
 "Summary":"Requires the department of health to consult with the office of addiction services and supports, the office for the prevention of domestic violence, and the department of veterans' services for purposes of administering the traumatic brain injury program and state policies with respect to traumatic brain injuries; adds the commissioner or executive director of such offices or departments to the traumatic brain injury services coordinating council.",
 "LawSection":"Public Health Law","LawCode":"Amd §§2740 & 2744, Pub Health L",
 "ActClause":"AN ACT to amend the public health law, in relation to the offices and departments that the department of health shall consult with for the traumatic brain injury program and to the designation of certain persons or their designees to the traumatic brain injury services coordinating council",
 "SameAsPrintNo":"S10216-2025"
